Package fs.fibu2.view.model

Class Summary
AccountInformation This is a simple, immutable string tuple class for representing account information fields by their ID.
AccountInformationListModel Implements a list model for the set of all account information fields.
AccountListModel Implements a list model for a sorted list of all accounts used in a journal.
AccountTableModel This class implements a model for a very small table containing information about account states at the beginning and the end of a certain JournalTableModel (or a connected subset of it)
BilancialAccountModel This model is created from a BilancialTreeModel and contains the values for all accounts used in that model.
BilancialInformation A BilancialInformation is an immutable tupel of bilancial sums for a fsfibu2 journal table row.
BilancialMapping A bilancial mapping is an ordered map from EntrySeparators to BilancialInformation.
BilancialTableModel This model contains the bilancial valued obtained from a BilancialTree.
BilancialTreeModel This class implements a tree model displaying the categories actually used in a journal (plus an additional child for each category which has subcategories AND entries directly in this category), modulo a certain filter.
BilancialTreeModel.ExtendedCategory This class represents a category, together with the additional information, whether this is a 'real' category node or the additional category node in the category itself (a boolean flag: It is true, when the object is the additional node)
CategoryListModel This class implements a simple list of categories of a journal.
ExportListModel Implements a simple list of JournalExport, sorted alphabetically by their name.
FilterListModel This class implements a list model for the filters available from the FilterLoader.
FilterPoolModel This class represents the filters available in the FilterPool of a given Journal.
JournalTableModel This class implements a model for a Journal table.
JournalTimeSeriesCollection This class implements a time series collection for an fsfibu 2 Journal.
ReadingPointModel Implements a list of reading points of a journal, sorted by date and afterwards by name
SeparatorModel This class models a list of displayed separators in a JournalTableModel.
StartValueModel This implements a table model which in the left column displays accounts of a Journal and in the right column allows the user to edit start values of these accounts.
TableModelComparator An instance of this class compares objects which are displayed in a journal table, i.e.
YearListModel This model represents a list of all years for which there are entries in a journal + a null object which represents 'all years'
YearSeparators This class keeps track of the default year separators necessary for a journal.
